comment.body: Can you investigate to see the cause of the individual errors?  If memory serves we turned `-fvisibility=hidden` on for a reason, to make sure we were exporting exactly the symbols we wanted to export.  So if that's not the case, I'd rather fix it than just turn the feature off.
